  <entry>
    <title>Python爬虫实战——外网爬取加页面滚动</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/</id>
    <published>2023-06-09T04:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-06-10T14:28:36.809Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="项目背景介绍">项目背景介绍</h1><p>我们想要研究国外的华语报刊和内地普通话报刊在词汇使用上的异同，因此首先我们需要对不同国家的报刊资料进行爬取。我们选定的国家为马来西亚，想要爬取的报刊网址为https://www.sinchew.com.my/和https://www.chinapress.com.my/，我们会在这两个网站上分别摘取一些文章，使得文章总篇数为100篇左右。同时对于内地的报刊，我们选用的是http://www.people.com.cn/和http://paper.news.cn/，同样爬取100篇左右的内容即可。几个网站的网页分别展示如下：</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_first_page.2g6lejzvscw0.webp" alt="星洲网首页图片"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">星洲网首页图片</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/chinapress_first_page.3enc7yua01u0.webp" alt="中国报首页"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">中国报首页</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/people_first_page.6p56zf8conw0.webp" alt="人民网首页"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">人民网首页</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/xinhua_first_page.5xe9ykmm29o0.webp" alt="新华社首页"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">新华社首页</figcaption></figure><h1 id="sinchew网站爬虫实战">sinchew网站爬虫实战</h1><p>第一个爬虫我将以requests+bs4为例做展示，需要导入的库为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先我们实现一个最基础的获取网页的框架：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url1 = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get html using header</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url1, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们将会发现以上代码是无法获得对应网站的响应的，无论当前主机上是否开启了代理，这是因为这个网站实际上是需要翻墙才能登录的，因此我们需要先考虑怎么使得爬虫能够识别代理。以我使用的Clash为例，我们可以从Clash的常规页面的第一项端口看到，这里使用的端口是7890：</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/Clash.2bj3v1vgz0w0.webp" alt="Clash常规页面"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">Clash常规页面</figcaption></figure><p>于是我们应该将以上代码修改为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url1 = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my/category/%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD/%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get html using header</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">proxies=&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;http&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;https&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url1, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实际上也就是添加了proxies参数而已，在这里proxies最后两项的7890应该修改为你对应的端口。</p><p>前面我们只算是完成了前期准备工作，要完成第一部分内容的爬取，我们首先需要获得对应的新闻网页链接，我们首先选择:zap:国内:bookmark:即时国内这个栏目，用小箭头点到对应的链接上，我们找到两个有较明显关系的层次（divclass="desc desc-desktop" 和 a class="internalLink"），展示如下：</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_crawl_select_page.1h5yk1yr2934.webp" alt="sinchew_crawl_select_page"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">sinchew_crawl_select_page</figcaption></figure><p>我们需要将其转为BeautifulSoup支持的select语法，同时将所有的href提取出来，也就是这么写：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">links = soup.select(<span class="string">&#x27;[class=&quot;desc desc-desktop&quot;] a[class=&quot;internalLink&quot;]&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">links = [link.get(<span class="string">&#x27;href&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> link <span class="keyword">in</span> links]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来就会展现一个文章列表，该列表存储的就是我们能得到的页面啦~</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_part1_code.5jspovyd8s00.webp" alt="sinchew_part1_code"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">sinchew_part1_code</figcaption></figure><p>但我们会发现，欸怎么只有这么几条，远远达不到我们想要拿到的数量呀，我们回到源网页看看，结果发现原来页面是下滑滚动加载的，我们点击Network下勾选XHR这个小标签，会发现这个部分一直有资源弹出。事实上是当我们向下滚动鼠标滑轮时，左侧栏内的数据包会实现自动加载，这是使用<a class="link" href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/AJAX/8425">Ajax<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>异步加载技术实现的。</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_roll_xhr.1tsgkcxr2qh.webp" alt="sinchew_roll_xhr"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">sinchew_roll_xhr</figcaption></figure><p>我们接下来可以点一下这些随着滚轮下滑新出现的数据包观察一下，我们立刻就会发现很有趣的事：</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/sinchew_cat_roll.76jx0xkdt000.webp" alt="sinchew_cat_roll"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">sinchew_cat_roll</figcaption></figure><p>这里很明目张胆地告诉了我们page=3，再往前面翻一下另一个带有<font color="#008000">?cat=471</font>字样的数据包，我们打开之后发现内容几乎没有改变，也仅仅只是page从3变成了2，这就告诉我们该请求的基准URL （由于还未拼接查询参数，所以称之为基准URL）为<font color="Blue">https://www.sinchew.com.my/ajx-api/category_posts/?cat=471</font>，且由后面的一连串东西我们至少能知道他们的查询参数具有如下规律：</p><blockquote><p>page: 控制页面</p><p>posts_per_page:控制每页显示的文章数量（这和我们前面爬取出来只有10篇文章非常符合）</p></blockquote><p>将这里的page设置为4之后直接在浏览器打开显示的结果如下：</p><figure><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/chenkai66/picx-images-hosting@master/20230610/cat_result.egsjdanz880.webp" alt="cat_result"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">cat_result</figcaption></figure><p>我们可以从这个列表中获得对应的permalink，这个就是我们最终需要的文章链接了。另外我其实试过能不能修改posts_per_page来使得直接查一次就能获取足够多的网页，但实际上没什么卵用，还是老老实实去爬吧。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
